        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 23. Gordonopsis phorcys, new species, holotype female (10.9 × 16.8 mm) (MNHN-IU-2008-12211), Solomon Islands. A, dorsal view of carapace showing relative P5 length; B, ventral view of cephalothorax showing coxae, basis-ischia, and pleon; C–F, right P2–P5, respectively (all to same scale); G, right P5 pseudochela; H, ventral view of cephalothorax showing sternopleonal cavity, coxae, and basis-ischia." ;
